.Dt LIBCERT 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm cert_config_issuer_c ,
.Nm cert_config_issuer_o ,
.Nm cert_config_issuer_ou ,
.Nm cert_config_issuer_dnq ,
.Nm cert_config_issuer_st ,
.Nm cert_config_issuer_cn ,
.Nm cert_config_issuer_ser ,
.Nm cert_config_subject_c ,
.Nm cert_config_subject_o ,
.Nm cert_config_subject_ou ,
.Nm cert_config_subject_dnq ,
.Nm cert_config_subject_st ,
.Nm cert_config_subject_cn ,
.Nm cert_config_subject_ser
.Nd certificate configuration context
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In cert.h
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_issuer_c "(struct cert_config *config, const char *c)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_issuer_o "(struct cert_config *, const char *o)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_issuer_ou "(struct cert_config *, const char *ou)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_issuer_dnq "(struct cert_config *, const char *dnq)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_issuer_st "(struct cert_config *, const char *st)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_issuer_cn "(struct cert_config *, const char *cn)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_issuer_ser "(struct cert_config *, const char *ser)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_subject_c "(struct cert_config *, const char *)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_subject_o "(struct cert_config *, const char *)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_subject_ou "(struct cert_config *, const char *)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_subject_dnq "(struct cert_config *, const char *)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_subject_st "(struct cert_config *, const char *)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_subject_cn "(struct cert_config *, const char *)"
.Ft void
.Fn cert_config_subject_ser "(struct cert_config *, const char *)"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn cert_config_issuer_c
function sets the issuer
.Dq country
to
.Ar c .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_issuer_o
function sets the issuer
.Dq organization
to
.Ar o .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_issuer_ou
function sets the issuer
.Dq organization unit
to
.Ar ou .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_issuer_dnq
function sets the issuer
.Dq distinguished name qualifier
to
.Ar dnq .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_issuer_st
function sets the issuer
.Dq state or province name
to
.Ar st .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_issuer_cn
function sets the issuer
.Dq common name
to
.Ar cn .
The default value is
.Dq localhost ,
if no other issuer name was set.
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_issuer_ser
function sets the issuer
.Dq serial number
to
.Ar ser .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_subject_c
function sets the subject
.Dq country
to
.Ar c .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_subject_o
function sets the subject
.Dq organization
to
.Ar o .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_subject_ou
function sets the subject
.Dq organization unit
to
.Ar ou .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_subject_dnq
function sets the subject
.Dq distinguished name qualifier
to
.Ar dnq .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_subject_st
function sets the subject
.Dq state or province name
to
.Ar st .
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_subject_cn
function sets the subject
.Dq common name
to
.Ar cn .
The default value is
.Dq localhost ,
if no other subject name was set.
.Pp
The
.Fn cert_config_subject_ser
function sets the subject
.Dq serial number
to
.Ar ser .
